{"type":"text","timestamp":1783411437696,"sessionID":"ses_0c4657dc0ffeLxhnWwpjfBEaEl","part":{"id":"prt_f3b9aeae5001plTZWjDnH4zgcj","messageID":"msg_f3b9ae147001wwJxGrdF3YvSir","sessionID":"ses_0c4657dc0ffeLxhnWwpjfBEaEl","type":"text","text":"```json\n{\n  \"anomaly_ids\": [],\n  \"answer\": \"根据现行《XX证券费用报销管理办法(2025修订版)》第五条的规定,单笔费用报销的审批权限统一按《XX证券授权管理办法》附件二执行。该附件二的费用报销审批权限表中,AR-03档位明确:单笔金额大于等于10000元(含)且小于50000元时,必要审批角色为部门总经理。因此,单笔费用报销达到10000元(含)需要部门总经理审批。\",\n  \"citations\": [\n    {\n      \"doc_id\": \"01_expense_reimbursement_2025.md\",\n      \"clause_no\": \"第五条\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"doc_id\": \"03_authorization_management.md\",\n      \"clause_no\": \"第二条\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"doc_id\": \"03_authorization_management.md\",\n      \"clause_no\": \"附件二\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```","time":{"start":1783411436261,"end":1783411437664}}}
